{"id":"the-brave-ladybug","slug":"the-brave-ladybug","title":"The Brave Ladybug","title_ko":"용감한 무당벌레","level":"A1","ageBand":"8-10","coverUrl":"/seed/the-brave-ladybug/cover.webp","summary_ko":"넓은 정원을 가로질러 길 잃은 동생을 찾아가는 작은 무당벌레의 용기.","wordCount":123,"pages":[{"id":"the-brave-ladybug-p1","pageNo":1,"spread":"p1","imageUrl":"/seed/the-brave-ladybug/p1.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-brave-ladybug-p1-s1","ord":0,"text":"Lily was a small red ladybug.","translation_ko":"릴리는 작고 빨간 무당벌레였어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-brave-ladybug/audio/p1-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Lily","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":760},{"word":"was","charStart":5,"charEnd":8,"startMs":760,"endMs":1080},{"word":"a","charStart":9,"charEnd":10,"startMs":1080,"endMs":1340},{"word":"small","charStart":11,"charEnd":16,"startMs":1340,"endMs":1680},{"word":"red","charStart":17,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1680,"endMs":1980},{"word":"ladybug","charStart":21,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1980,"endMs":2440}]},{"id":"the-brave-ladybug-p1-s2","ord":1,"text":"She had black spots and a kind heart.","translation_ko":"검은 점이 있고 마음씨가 고운 아이였죠.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-brave-ladybug/audio/p1-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"She","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":320},{"word":"had","charStart":4,"charEnd":7,"startMs":320,"endMs":640},{"word":"black","charStart":8,"charEnd":13,"startMs":640,"endMs":1060},{"word":"spots","charStart":14,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1060,"endMs":1440},{"word":"and","charStart":20,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1440,"endMs":1740},{"word":"a","charStart":24,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1740,"endMs":2040},{"word":"kind","charStart":26,"charEnd":30,"startMs":2040,"endMs":2200},{"word":"heart","charStart":31,"charEnd":36,"startMs":2200,"endMs":2520}]}]},{"id":"the-brave-ladybug-p2","pageNo":2,"spread":"p2","imageUrl":"/seed/the-brave-ladybug/p2.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-brave-ladybug-p2-s1","ord":0,"text":"One morning, her little brother was gone.","translation_ko":"어느 아침, 동생이 사라졌어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-brave-ladybug/audio/p2-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"One","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":300},{"word":"morning","charStart":4,"charEnd":11,"startMs":300,"endMs":700},{"word":"her","charStart":13,"charEnd":16,"startMs":800,"endMs":1360},{"word":"little","charStart":17,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1360,"endMs":1600},{"word":"brother","charStart":24,"charEnd":31,"startMs":1600,"endMs":1840},{"word":"was","charStart":32,"charEnd":35,"startMs":1840,"endMs":2420},{"word":"gone","charStart":36,"charEnd":40,"startMs":2420,"endMs":2620}]},{"id":"the-brave-ladybug-p2-s2","ord":1,"text":"\"I must find him,\" she said.","translation_ko":"\"내가 꼭 찾아야 해.\" 릴리가 말했어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-brave-ladybug/audio/p2-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"I","charStart":1,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":180},{"word":"must","charStart":3,"charEnd":7,"startMs":180,"endMs":600},{"word":"find","charStart":8,"charEnd":12,"startMs":600,"endMs":960},{"word":"him","charStart":13,"charEnd":16,"startMs":960,"endMs":1720},{"word":"she","charStart":19,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1720,"endMs":1900},{"word":"said","charStart":23,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1900,"endMs":2160}]}]},{"id":"the-brave-ladybug-p3","pageNo":3,"spread":"p3","imageUrl":"/seed/the-brave-ladybug/p3.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-brave-ladybug-p3-s1","ord":0,"text":"The garden was very big and wide.","translation_ko":"정원은 아주 크고 넓었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-brave-ladybug/audio/p3-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"The","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":880},{"word":"garden","charStart":4,"charEnd":10,"startMs":880,"endMs":1100},{"word":"was","charStart":11,"charEnd":14,"startMs":1100,"endMs":1440},{"word":"very","charStart":15,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1440,"endMs":1720},{"word":"big","charStart":20,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1720,"endMs":2020},{"word":"and","charStart":24,"charEnd":27,"startMs":2020,"endMs":2320},{"word":"wide","charStart":28,"charEnd":32,"startMs":2320,"endMs":2540}]},{"id":"the-brave-ladybug-p3-s2","ord":1,"text":"But Lily was brave, so she began to walk.","translation_ko":"하지만 릴리는 용감했고, 그래서 걷기 시작했죠.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-brave-ladybug/audio/p3-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"But","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":540},{"word":"Lily","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":540,"endMs":740},{"word":"was","charStart":9,"charEnd":12,"startMs":740,"endMs":1060},{"word":"brave","charStart":13,"charEnd":18,"startMs":1060,"endMs":1440},{"word":"so","charStart":20,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1940,"endMs":2080},{"word":"she","charStart":23,"charEnd":26,"startMs":2080,"endMs":2320},{"word":"began","charStart":27,"charEnd":32,"startMs":2320,"endMs":2560},{"word":"to","charStart":33,"charEnd":35,"startMs":2560,"endMs":2900},{"word":"walk","charStart":36,"charEnd":40,"startMs":2900,"endMs":3120}]}]},{"id":"the-brave-ladybug-p4","pageNo":4,"spread":"p4","imageUrl":"/seed/the-brave-ladybug/p4.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-brave-ladybug-p4-s1","ord":0,"text":"First she came to a big dewdrop.","translation_ko":"먼저 커다란 이슬방울을 만났어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-brave-ladybug/audio/p4-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"First","charStart":0,"charEnd":5,"startMs":0,"endMs":500},{"word":"she","charStart":6,"charEnd":9,"startMs":920,"endMs":1100},{"word":"came","charStart":10,"charEnd":14,"startMs":1100,"endMs":1300},{"word":"to","charStart":15,"charEnd":17,"startMs":1300,"endMs":1520},{"word":"a","charStart":18,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1520,"endMs":1620},{"word":"big","charStart":20,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1620,"endMs":1920},{"word":"dewdrop","charStart":24,"charEnd":31,"startMs":1920,"endMs":2420}]},{"id":"the-brave-ladybug-p4-s2","ord":1,"text":"It was round and shiny like glass.","translation_ko":"유리처럼 동그랗고 반짝였죠.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-brave-ladybug/audio/p4-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"It","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":140},{"word":"was","charStart":3,"charEnd":6,"startMs":140,"endMs":420},{"word":"round","charStart":7,"charEnd":12,"startMs":420,"endMs":800},{"word":"and","charStart":13,"charEnd":16,"startMs":800,"endMs":1180},{"word":"shiny","charStart":17,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1180,"endMs":1440},{"word":"like","charStart":23,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1440,"endMs":1860},{"word":"glass","charStart":28,"charEnd":33,"startMs":1860,"endMs":2200}]}]},{"id":"the-brave-ladybug-p5","pageNo":5,"spread":"p5","imageUrl":"/seed/the-brave-ladybug/p5.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-brave-ladybug-p5-s1","ord":0,"text":"Lily was afraid, but she jumped over it.","translation_ko":"릴리는 무서웠지만, 폴짝 뛰어넘었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-brave-ladybug/audio/p5-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Lily","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":700},{"word":"was","charStart":5,"charEnd":8,"startMs":700,"endMs":960},{"word":"afraid","charStart":9,"charEnd":15,"startMs":960,"endMs":1340},{"word":"but","charStart":17,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1600,"endMs":1720},{"word":"she","charStart":21,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1720,"endMs":1980},{"word":"jumped","charStart":25,"charEnd":31,"startMs":1980,"endMs":2240},{"word":"over","charStart":32,"charEnd":36,"startMs":2240,"endMs":2500},{"word":"it","charStart":37,"charEnd":39,"startMs":2500,"endMs":2700}]}]},{"id":"the-brave-ladybug-p6","pageNo":6,"spread":"p6","imageUrl":"/seed/the-brave-ladybug/p6.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-brave-ladybug-p6-s1","ord":0,"text":"Then she saw a tall green stem.","translation_ko":"그다음 키 큰 초록 줄기를 보았어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-brave-ladybug/audio/p6-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Then","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":420},{"word":"she","charStart":5,"charEnd":8,"startMs":420,"endMs":760},{"word":"saw","charStart":9,"charEnd":12,"startMs":760,"endMs":980},{"word":"a","charStart":13,"charEnd":14,"startMs":980,"endMs":1380},{"word":"tall","charStart":15,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1380,"endMs":1540},{"word":"green","charStart":20,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1540,"endMs":1960},{"word":"stem","charStart":26,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1960,"endMs":2260}]},{"id":"the-brave-ladybug-p6-s2","ord":1,"text":"It went up and up into the sky.","translation_ko":"줄기는 하늘 높이 쭉쭉 뻗어 있었죠.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-brave-ladybug/audio/p6-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"It","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":240},{"word":"went","charStart":3,"charEnd":7,"startMs":240,"endMs":500},{"word":"up","charStart":8,"charEnd":10,"startMs":500,"endMs":900},{"word":"and","charStart":11,"charEnd":14,"startMs":900,"endMs":1360},{"word":"up","charStart":15,"charEnd":17,"startMs":1360,"endMs":1620},{"word":"into","charStart":18,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1620,"endMs":2060},{"word":"the","charStart":23,"charEnd":26,"startMs":2060,"endMs":2360},{"word":"sky","charStart":27,"charEnd":30,"startMs":2360,"endMs":2600}]}]},{"id":"the-brave-ladybug-p7","pageNo":7,"spread":"p7","imageUrl":"/seed/the-brave-ladybug/p7.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-brave-ladybug-p7-s1","ord":0,"text":"Slowly, she climbed to the very top.","translation_ko":"릴리는 천천히 꼭대기까지 올라갔어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-brave-ladybug/audio/p7-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Slowly","charStart":0,"charEnd":6,"startMs":0,"endMs":580},{"word":"she","charStart":8,"charEnd":11,"startMs":800,"endMs":1280},{"word":"climbed","charStart":12,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1280,"endMs":1620},{"word":"to","charStart":20,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1620,"endMs":1840},{"word":"the","charStart":23,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1840,"endMs":1980},{"word":"very","charStart":27,"charEnd":31,"startMs":1980,"endMs":2360},{"word":"top","charStart":32,"charEnd":35,"startMs":2360,"endMs":2620}]},{"id":"the-brave-ladybug-p7-s2","ord":1,"text":"From there she could see far away.","translation_ko":"그곳에서는 멀리까지 보였어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-brave-ladybug/audio/p7-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"From","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":260},{"word":"there","charStart":5,"charEnd":10,"startMs":260,"endMs":580},{"word":"she","charStart":11,"charEnd":14,"startMs":860,"endMs":1040},{"word":"could","charStart":15,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1040,"endMs":1240},{"word":"see","charStart":21,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1240,"endMs":1420},{"word":"far","charStart":25,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1420,"endMs":1920},{"word":"away","charStart":29,"charEnd":33,"startMs":1920,"endMs":2140}]}]},{"id":"the-brave-ladybug-p8","pageNo":8,"spread":"p8","imageUrl":"/seed/the-brave-ladybug/p8.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-brave-ladybug-p8-s1","ord":0,"text":"\"There you are!\" Lily called with joy.","translation_ko":"\"거기 있었구나!\" 릴리가 기뻐서 외쳤어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-brave-ladybug/audio/p8-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"There","charStart":1,"charEnd":6,"startMs":0,"endMs":480},{"word":"you","charStart":7,"charEnd":10,"startMs":480,"endMs":900},{"word":"are","charStart":11,"charEnd":14,"startMs":900,"endMs":1400},{"word":"Lily","charStart":17,"charEnd":21,"startMs":2000,"endMs":2120},{"word":"called","charStart":22,"charEnd":28,"startMs":2120,"endMs":2460},{"word":"with","charStart":29,"charEnd":33,"startMs":2460,"endMs":2740},{"word":"joy","charStart":34,"charEnd":37,"startMs":2740,"endMs":3020}]},{"id":"the-brave-ladybug-p8-s2","ord":1,"text":"Her little brother was on a yellow leaf.","translation_ko":"동생은 노란 잎 위에 있었죠.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-brave-ladybug/audio/p8-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Her","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":200},{"word":"little","charStart":4,"charEnd":10,"startMs":200,"endMs":500},{"word":"brother","charStart":11,"charEnd":18,"startMs":500,"endMs":740},{"word":"was","charStart":19,"charEnd":22,"startMs":740,"endMs":1020},{"word":"on","charStart":23,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1020,"endMs":1180},{"word":"a","charStart":26,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1180,"endMs":1420},{"word":"yellow","charStart":28,"charEnd":34,"startMs":1420,"endMs":1620},{"word":"leaf","charStart":35,"charEnd":39,"startMs":1620,"endMs":1980}]}]},{"id":"the-brave-ladybug-p9","pageNo":9,"spread":"p9","imageUrl":"/seed/the-brave-ladybug/p9.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-brave-ladybug-p9-s1","ord":0,"text":"They flew home together, side by side.","translation_ko":"둘은 나란히 함께 집으로 날아갔어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-brave-ladybug/audio/p9-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"They","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":300},{"word":"flew","charStart":5,"charEnd":9,"startMs":300,"endMs":560},{"word":"home","charStart":10,"charEnd":14,"startMs":560,"endMs":920},{"word":"together","charStart":15,"charEnd":23,"startMs":920,"endMs":1320},{"word":"side","charStart":25,"charEnd":29,"startMs":1460,"endMs":2000},{"word":"by","charStart":30,"charEnd":32,"startMs":2000,"endMs":2300},{"word":"side","charStart":33,"charEnd":37,"startMs":2300,"endMs":2560}]},{"id":"the-brave-ladybug-p9-s2","ord":1,"text":"A small ladybug can be very brave.","translation_ko":"작은 무당벌레도 아주 용감할 수 있답니다.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-brave-ladybug/audio/p9-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"A","charStart":0,"charEnd":1,"startMs":0,"endMs":460},{"word":"small","charStart":2,"charEnd":7,"startMs":460,"endMs":760},{"word":"ladybug","charStart":8,"charEnd":15,"startMs":760,"endMs":1240},{"word":"can","charStart":16,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1240,"endMs":1500},{"word":"be","charStart":20,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1500,"endMs":1680},{"word":"very","charStart":23,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1680,"endMs":2080},{"word":"brave","charStart":28,"charEnd":33,"startMs":2080,"endMs":2420}]}]}],"quiz":[{"question_ko":"릴리는 어떤 곤충인가요?","type":"mc","options":["갈색 개미","노란 나비","작고 빨간 무당벌레","초록 메뚜기"],"answerIndex":2,"explain_ko":"릴리는 검은 점이 있는 작고 빨간 무당벌레예요.","id":"the-brave-ladybug-q1","ord":0},{"question_ko":"릴리가 정원을 가로지른 까닭은 무엇인가요?","type":"mc","options":["집을 지으려고","사라진 동생을 찾으려고","친구와 놀려고","꽃을 따려고"],"answerIndex":1,"explain_ko":"어느 아침 동생이 사라져서 릴리가 찾아 나섰어요.","id":"the-brave-ladybug-q2","ord":1},{"question_ko":"릴리가 가장 먼저 만난 것은 무엇인가요?","type":"mc","options":["커다란 이슬방울","키 큰 줄기","노란 잎","작은 돌"],"answerIndex":0,"explain_ko":"릴리는 먼저 유리처럼 반짝이는 큰 이슬방울을 만났어요.","id":"the-brave-ladybug-q3","ord":2},{"question_ko":"릴리는 동생을 어디에서 찾았나요?","type":"mc","options":["노란 잎 위에서","꽃잎 아래에서","이슬방울 안에서","땅속에서"],"answerIndex":0,"explain_ko":"줄기 꼭대기에서 보니 동생이 노란 잎 위에 있었어요.","id":"the-brave-ladybug-q4","ord":3},{"question_ko":"이 이야기가 주는 교훈은 무엇인가요?","type":"mc","options":["작아도 용감할 수 있다","혼자가 더 편하다","정원은 위험하다","빨리 달려야 이긴다"],"answerIndex":0,"explain_ko":"작은 무당벌레도 동생을 위해 용기를 냈어요.","id":"the-brave-ladybug-q5","ord":4}]}